hints.description: This global company specializes in developing and manufacturing a wide range of rigid and flexible packaging solutions for the food, beverage, pharmaceutical, medical, and personal care industries. They create everything from plastic bottles and flexible pouches to cardboard boxes and specialized containers, focusing on sustainability and innovation in packaging design. CEO Ron *** has led the company through significant acquisitions and a focus on high-growth markets.
hints.funFact1: In 2019, the company completed a massive acquisition of Bemis, a deal valued at over $*** billion, significantly expanding its global footprint and product portfolio.
hints.funFact2: The company's origins trace back to 1860 in Melbourne, Australia, initially as a paper bag manufacturing business before evolving into the packaging giant it is today.
